  # Installation
  
  The easiest way to install Zulu is with its install script:
  
  ```sh
  curl -L https://zulu.molovo.co/install | zsh && zsh
  ```
  
  If you’d rather download and inspect the script before running it manually, follow these steps:
  
  ```sh
  git clone https://github.com/zulu-zsh/install
  cd install
  ./install
  ```
